Summary       Required or Optional?  Optional    Where?  In any property subschema, at the same level as  type .     The  prettyName  keyword can optionally appear on any property. If it does appear, it is used by the UI as a title for the UI widget associated with the property. If it does not appear, then the name of the property is used.  In this example, the user would see "Name of Database" on the UI, instead of just "name".  { 
